
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-mccann-session-policy-framework-using-eap-07.txt'>
    <title>"Session Policy Framework using EAP", Stephen McCann, Michael Montemurro</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-mccann-session-policy-framework-using-eap-07.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies a framework for implementing a session policy channel using EAP. It defines a standard mechanism by which a mobile device can conduct a session policy exchange with a policy network component, using EAP as a lower layer protocol, to obtain session policies. EAP Re-authentication Protocol is suggested as a mechanism to allow asynchronous use of SIP at upper layers.</description>
    <dc:date>2013-01-07T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
